### Base URL via API Gateway (Docker)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/api

### List notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications

### Get notification by id
@id = 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{id}}

### Create notification (admin/test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "achatId": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "userName": "John Doe",
  "ticketId": 1,
  "ticketDescription": "Optional description for the ticket 1",
  "trajetId": 1,
  "nomTrajet": "Ligne A",
  "cityName": "Sale",
  "priceInDhs": 5.50,
  "achatCreatedAt": "2025-11-15T09:39:15"
}

### Update notification (admin/test)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "Jane Doe",
  "cityName": "Rabat",
  "priceInDhs": 6.00
}

### Delete notification (admin/test)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{id}}
